    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After 20 years of eating nothing but porridge, Hank decides to collect ingredients for a nice tasty soup.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple side-scroller where the goal of each stage is to pick up the soup ingredient at the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 3 soups to collect ingredients for, each with a unique set of levels, including:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -Leek &amp; Potato soup, set in Onion Forest, teeming with curious wildlife </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -Lobster Bisque, set in Crab Coast, where soft sands border a shimmering ocean</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -Pumpkin soup, set in Pumpkin Hollow, a dark haunted valley where few dare to venture</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 8 challenges to complete per soup</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Unlockable game modes including time trial mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Level editor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created entirely by me, Sean T.</p>",
